long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Catch The Cat is an entertaining and fast-paced game available as a Chrome extension. Your mission is to catch a mischievous cat that's constantly on the move. As the cat dashes around the screen, you must use your reflexes and quick thinking to click on it before it escapes. Be careful not to click on other objects, as it will cost you points. 
With its colorful graphics, lively animations, and challenging gameplay, Catch The Cat offers a thrilling and addictive experience. Test your hand-eye coordination, compete for high scores, and unlock new levels as you progress. Whether you're a casual gamer or seeking a fun time-killer, Catch The Cat on Chrome Extension guarantees hours of feline-catching excitement. Get ready to pounce on the fast-moving cat and prove your agility in this engaging game.
